<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pages</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" 
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>
<body class="p-2 text-white" style="background-color: #684551;">
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark" style="background-color: #684551;">
            <div class="container-fluid">
              <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">Pages Bookstore</a>
              <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="true" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
              </button>
              <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                  <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                  </li>
                  <form class="d-flex fixed-right" action="/view" method="GET">
                    <button class="btn btn-outline-dark" type="submit">View Orders</button>
                  </form>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="alert alert-dark m-5" role="alert">
            <h4 class="alert-heading">Well done!</h4>
            <p>Thank you for placing your order! We will ready the book for your pick up at your latest convenience. We will also be sending you an email with the confirmation and the price and details of the book whenever it's available at our store</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="mb-0">Hope you have a great read!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
